# Smart Traffic Prediction & Congestion Management System

The Smart Traffic Prediction & Congestion Management System** is an AI-powered traffic management platform designed to monitor real-time traffic conditions, predict congestion using Machine Learning, optimize travel routes, generate intelligent alerts, and provide interactive analytics dashboards. The system aims to reduce traffic congestion, improve travel efficiency, and support smart city transportation initiatives.

## Project Objective

The objective of this project is to develop an intelligent traffic management system that can:

* Monitor real-time traffic conditions
* Predict traffic congestion using Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning
* Analyze traffic flow and peak-hour traffic patterns
* Recommend optimized travel routes
* Generate congestion and emergency alerts
* Visualize traffic insights through interactive dashboards

## Key Features

* User Authentication & Role-Based Access
* Real-Time Traffic Monitoring
* AI-Based Traffic Prediction
* Congestion Detection
* Route Optimization & Travel Time Estimation
* Smart Alert & Notification System
* Interactive Traffic Analytics Dashboard
* Machine Learning Prediction Models
* Historical Traffic Analysis
* Responsive User Interface

